wsintelliauction.lib.gui
Class WindowHandle

java.lang.Object
  wsintelliauction.lib.gui.WindowHandle
Direct Known Subclasses:
MainWindowHandle
public abstract class WindowHandle
extends java.lang.Object

Window handle super class. Each window is paired with a window handle, which the window uses for handling of all window events (such as button pressed events, input data change event, button selected events, scroll events, etc) and then submits an associated task to the task manager for further handling.

James Lewis
